trans-unit.source: Represents a container for bitmap frames.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en beholder for punktgrafikk for forhandleren.

trans-unit.source: Each bitmap frame is a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Imaging.BitmapSource"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hver punktgrafikk ramme er en <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Imaging.BitmapSource"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This abstract class provides a base set of functionality for all derived decoder objects.
trans-unit.target: Denne abstrakte klassen gir et grunnleggende sett med funksjoner for alle avledede dekoderen-objekter.

trans-unit.source: BitmapDecoder is not a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.BitmapFrame> itself; rather, it is a container for <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.BitmapFrame> objects.
trans-unit.target: BitmapDecoder er ikke en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.BitmapFrame>selve; i stedet den er en beholder for <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.BitmapFrame>objekter.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.BitmapFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.BitmapFrame>

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.BitmapFrame> in the container can potentially have different attributes, including different sizes, resolutions, or palettes.
trans-unit.target: Hver <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.BitmapFrame>i beholderen kan har ulike attributter, inkludert ulik størrelse, løsninger eller palettene.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.BitmapFrame>

trans-unit.source: Unless a specific codec is selected, [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] uses automatic run-time discovery to identify the format of an image and match it with the appropriate codec.
trans-unit.target: Med mindre en bestemt kodek er merket, [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] bruker automatisk kjøretid søking til å identifisere formatet på et bilde og samsvarer med den riktige kodeken.

trans-unit.source: This discovery process allows a codec developed by an [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_isv](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-isv-md.md)] to be automatically discoverable by the system.
trans-unit.target: Denne prosessen for oppdaging gjør det mulig for en kodek utviklet av en [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_isv](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-isv-md.md)] automatisk synlig av systemet.

trans-unit.source: To select a specific codec, the derived BitmapDecoder or <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.BitmapEncoder>, such as the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffBitmapDecoder> class, should be used.
trans-unit.target: Velge en bestemt kodek, avledede BitmapDecoder eller <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.BitmapEncoder>, som den <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffBitmapDecoder>klasse, må brukes.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.TiffBitmapDecoder> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.BitmapEncoder>

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_tiff](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-tiff-md.md)] and [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_gif](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-gif-md.md)] are the only implemented image formats that support multiple frames.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_tiff](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-tiff-md.md)]og [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_gif](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-gif-md.md)] er de eneste implementert bildeformater som støtter flere bilder.
